To run the script please do the following:

1) Create a folder called polyMesh at the root of the script

2) Copy files that was generated by snappyHexMesh to the folder: boundary,
                                                                 faces,
                                                                 neighbour,
                                                                 owner,
                                                                 points

3) Check whether there is a folder called Output since the results will be
   written there

4) open the terminal at the script root folder and type the following command:
   python2.7 Translator.py

WARNING:   At some systems you have to explicitly point out the path
           to the Python interpreter
            EXAMPLE: /usr/bin/python2.7 Translator.py


